snippet.title: Alexis Arc  Heroes of the Three Kingdoms official Callista path gameplay | AlphaDio Production
snippet.description:
Finally I finish my second path of Alexis Arc!
Callista is very good at support and ranged attack. With this release, version 2.0, I also fix many bugs in Auria path.
With this release, I have one last path to work with: Deminia
Product Link: https://alphadio-production.itch.io/alexis-arc-heroes-of-the-three-kingdoms

AlphaDio Production, Indonesia
